Class Matrix_Column_Permutation

  • java.lang.Object
    • jed.Matrix_Column_Permutation

  • public class Matrix_Column_Permutation
extends java.lang.Object
    JED class Matrix_Column_Permutation: Randomizes a matrix by permuting its columns. Each column is permuted using the same random 'mapping'. This preserves the orthonormality of eigenvectors.
